title: Spanish Springs volleyballer honored as Athlete of the Week
text: Facebook Email Twitter Google+ LinkedIn Pinterest Spanish Springs volleyballer honored as Athlete of the Week Sami Szachara, a senior at Spanish Springs who plays middle blocker on the Cougars’ volleyball team, had 10 kills and three blocks in the Cougars’ 3-0 win over Reed on Tuesday. The Cougars play at McQueen on Thursday for the league championship.
